n my pc) and your timer is reset.<br><br>Now I ALWAYS know when mend is due.  Hope you find it as useful as I do.<br><br>The link to the counter mod itself is here (SS and download):<br><br>http://equi.freeservers.com/timer.html<br><br><br>Mitch<br><br>ps Mods I considered putting it in new features section but wanted to make sure everyone saw this as its monk specific and I know some peeps dont check that section, feel free to move it) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umitchtheblonde.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mitch The Blonde</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://megablonde.freewebspace.com/rbt-hex.gif" BORDER=0> at: 8/17/02 8:17:52 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fder</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 2651<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(8/15/02 4:34:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=239.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://mickeyd.freewebspace.com/Images/Aim.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bind Wounds Timer in new UI</span><hr size=1> Lots of people go to new features.  Its our second most popular forum. <p><table width="100%" border="0" height="90">  <tr>     <td width="5%" height="98"><img src=http://mickeyd.freewebspace.com/Images/Fderlgo.gif></td>    <td width="100%" height="98"><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1349">FDER       FRENZY</a></b> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_